"{\"uid\": \"nypost.com-2024-05-29-lifestyle-the-surprising-truth-about-the-olympic-games-anti-sex-beds\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"They will not be getting gold medals for abstinence.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes hoping to get frisky during the upcoming Olympic Games in Paris appeared to have their dreams dashed after organizers announced they wereordering the same \\\"anti-sex\\\" beds used at the 2020 Tokyo Games.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 263, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 121, \"end\": 126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.402550565428668e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the 16,000 modular mattresses made by Japanese companyAirweaveand sent to the City of Love ahead of the opening ceremony on July 26aresafe for sex, The Post can reveal.\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 307, \"end\": 315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.9992660018835837, \"rank\": 0.0006859620736401259, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Photographs of the twin-size mattresses - made of polyethylene and set up on cardboard bed frames - recently raised eyebrows, with many speculating they were designed to deter any amorous activity.\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 636, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, looks can be deceiving.\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 670, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Airweave US' Chief Operating Officer Brett Thornton told The Post that the cardboard frames are even \\\"designed far sturdier than typical wooden bed frames,\\\" meaning athletes can go for the gold on the mattresses night after night.\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 902, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 681, \"end\": 683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9779142304507201, \"rank\": 0.022576332548186504, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When pressed to confirm whether or not the competitors can have sex on the beds, a rep for Thornton pointed to a statement originally given tothe Japan Timesby Airwave CEO Motokuni Takaoka.\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 1093, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 995, \"end\": 1003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trent_Thornton\", \"score\": 0.9980339719548865, \"rank\": 0.0007841291720613939, \"text\": \"Thornton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trent_Thornton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trent_Thornton\"}, {\"begin\": 1050, \"end\": 1055, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9999919149508393, \"rank\": 6.623739733728505e-06, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 1085, \"end\": 1092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Takaoka_Castle\", \"score\": 0.9888289312135231, \"rank\": 0.01118481006826426, \"text\": \"Takaoka\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q23413\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Takaoka_Castle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Takaoka_Castle\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sex is sex, whether it's on our mattress or somebody else's,\\\" Takaoka told the publication.\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1187, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We just wanted to create a mattress that is stronger than normal mattress.\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1263, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are only focused on sleep; we are not concerned with anything else that happens on the bed.\\\"\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1359, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Airweave has been working with Olympic athletes since the 2008 Games in Beijing but became an official partner for the Tokyo Games in 2020.\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1433, \"end\": 1440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9995148841616797, \"rank\": 0.00048532796952301544, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At that Games, organizers implemented an\\\"intimacy ban\\\"amid the COVID pandemic.\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1580, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1565, \"end\": 1579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"score\": 0.9999998699991095, \"rank\": 1.2487803084473004e-07, \"text\": \"COVID pandemic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Airweave beds were subsequently dubbed \\\"anti-sex\\\" - a term that gained traction given their twin size and the fact they were made of polyethylene.\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1732, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While the Airweave mattresses may not look ideal for lovemaking, they are said to be surprisingly comfortable, ensuring every athlete gets seriously good sleep.\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1894, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Each mattress is comprised of three separate blocks that come in varying grades of firmness (firm, moderate and soft) so they can be customized for different body types.\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 2065, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Upon arrival at the Olympic Village, each athlete will be scanned by an artificial intelligence-powered app so that they can have a mattress made to match their needs.\", \"from\": 2067, \"to\": 2234, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For instance, most swimmers have a lean build, meaning their mattress will most likely be comprised of three soft blocks.\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2357, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rugby players, on the other hand, have a build that usually requires a firm block in the middle.\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2455, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Airweave said that studies have shown that their mattress' polyethylene material \\\"promotes deeper, quality sleep by allowing better distribution of weight, effortless turning and optimal spinal alignment.\\\"\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2662, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, the company claimed polyethylene has been \\\"scientifically proven\\\" to result in deep sleep that lasts 308% longer than that which occurs on a regular memory foam mattress.\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2845, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During the Tokyo Games, American fencer Katharine Holmes claimed that the mattresses were comfortable compared to other beds she had slept on while traveling for competitions.\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 3022, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2871, \"end\": 2879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999731808206, \"rank\": 1.8267928807795644e-08, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2887, \"end\": 2903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katharine_Holmes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katharine Holmes\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katharine_Holmes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katharine_Holmes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not wake up in the middle of the night in screaming agony,\\\"\\u00a0she stated, defending the Airweave products in an interview withBusiness Insider.\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3171, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, the mattress blocks are entirely washable and hypoallergenic, meaning there will not be any worry about bedbugs infesting the Olympic Village.\", \"from\": 3173, \"to\": 3329, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3313, \"end\": 3328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.457279750874582e-24, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's of particular relief, given thatParis was plagued by the parasiteslast summer.\", \"from\": 3331, \"to\": 3416, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, the mattresses are 100% recyclable, meaning they are perfect for Olympic organizers, who have sustainability at top of mind.\", \"from\": 3418, \"to\": 3553, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I hope that Paris 2024's efforts to reduce its impact will show that it is possible to do things differently,\\\" Georgina Grenon, director of environmental excellence for the organizing committee, recently told theAFP.\", \"from\": 3555, \"to\": 3772, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3568, \"end\": 3578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.585557418596952e-14, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the Airweave mattress will withstand wild nights of sex, amorous athletes do not require beds to get bawdy.\", \"from\": 3774, \"to\": 3887, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the years, stories about wild romps among Olympians have abounded in the media - and the sizzling sex sessions seemingly take place anywhere and everywhere.\", \"from\": 3889, \"to\": 4050, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ESPNquoted one kinky competitor as saying they had sex on a balcony at the 2004 Games in Athens before being busted by a fellow athlete.\", \"from\": 4052, \"to\": 4188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4141, \"end\": 4147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9735059331440994, \"rank\": 0.027215104859364694, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile,the Mirrorreported that an orgy occurred among Olympians in a hot tub one year.\", \"from\": 4190, \"to\": 4279, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The same publication also cited one two-time gold medalist as saying: \\\"I have seen people having sex right out in the open.\", \"from\": 4281, \"to\": 4404, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On the grass, between buildings, people are getting down and dirty.\\\"\", \"from\": 4405, \"to\": 4473, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Organizers are anticipating that this year's competitors will be as horny as ever,ordering 300,000 condomsto be delivered to the Olympic Village alongside the Airweave beds.\", \"from\": 4475, \"to\": 4648, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4604, \"end\": 4619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.457279750874582e-24, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement\", \"from\": 4650, \"to\": 4663, \"entities\": []}]}"